cross-cultural perspectives.

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:24.980
What this experience
is like and how

00:07:24.980 --> 00:07:27.170
we think about disability
and citizenship

00:07:27.170 --> 00:07:30.355
not only here in the US,
but around the world.

00:07:30.355 --> 00:07:31.730
We'll really think
about how this

00:07:31.730 --> 00:07:33.890
