even outside of the live stream

00:07:39.710 --> 00:07:41.210
and really thinking
about how we can

00:07:41.210 --> 00:07:45.140
impact what's going on in our
world in such a dynamic time.

00:07:45.140 --> 00:07:46.880
And we'll get to
ask hard questions,

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:49.190
like what can really
be done to elevate

00:07:49.190 --> 00:07:51.620
our voice as a
disability community,

00:07:51.620 --> 00:07:54.410
and be taken seriously in this
national and international

00:07:54.410 --> 00:07:57.400
discourse around
diversity and inclusion?

00:07:57.400 --> 00:08:01.560
