of the outcomes of that law

00:09:11.660 --> 00:09:13.730
and all the advocacy
that came around

00:09:13.730 --> 00:09:20.144
in enacting it and bringing it
to its impact across cultures.

00:09:20.144 --> 00:09:21.560
