And so Tom is the
person who's going

00:16:35.060 --> 00:16:37.090
to be leading the
questions, and I

00:16:37.090 --> 00:16:39.340
think we're going to be
speaking for about 30 minutes,

00:16:39.340 --> 00:16:41.430
and then opening this
up for discussion

00:16:41.430 --> 00:16:43.110
for about 15 minutes.

00:16:43.110 --> 00:16:46.260
So I really hope
that you're thinking

00:16:46.260 --> 00:16:49.390
about comments you want to
