00:58:24.020 --> 00:58:27.020
My name is Joanne
Daniels Fiengold.

00:58:27.020 --> 00:58:30.230
I just want to put a
few things out there.

00:58:30.230 --> 00:58:32.220
Even though I've lived
in one for 16 years,

00:58:32.220 --> 00:58:36.860
I'm not in favor of senior
and disabled housing.

00:58:36.860 --> 00:58:40.370
I don't like being
segregated that way.

00:58:40.370 --> 00:58:42.020
There are far too
many people where

00:58:42.020 --> 00:58:46.700
I grew up in New Jersey who
had survived the concentration

00:58:46.700 --> 00:58:47.210
camps.

00:58:47.210 --> 00:58:53.640
I don't like the idea of
being marginalized that way.

00:58:53.640 --> 00:58:55.890
I want to speak to you to.

00:58:55.890 --> 00:59:01.150
Go out into the community, seek
out organizations that work

00:59:01.150 --> 00:59:03.670
with disabled people.

00:59:03.670 --> 00:59:07.860
I work at GBLS, Greater
Boston Legal Services.

00:59:07.860 --> 00:59:11.290
I volunteer with the children's
Disabilities Project.

00:59:11.290 --> 00:59:13.780
And quite a few of the
parents who are refugees

00:59:13.780 --> 00:59:15.820
don't want the
stigma of disability

00:59:15.820 --> 00:59:18.400
attached to their child,
even though the child needs

00:59:18.400 --> 00:59:20.230
services.

00:59:20.230 --> 00:59:22.046
And this is a big problem.

00:59:22.046 --> 00:59:24.670
But that's one of the ways that
you can, that's two of the ways

00:59:24.670 --> 00:59:27.552
that you can get
involved and bring people

00:59:27.552 --> 00:59:28.510
into what you're doing.

00:59:31.720 --> 00:59:33.760
Again, some people
might recognize

00:59:33.760 --> 00:59:36.570
my last name Daniels Feingold.

00:59:36.570 --> 00:59:39.850
I was the first named
plaintiff in the T access case

00:59:39.850 --> 00:59:43.430
