00:59:43.430 --> 00:59:45.430
Things are better,
but not perfect

00:59:45.430 --> 00:59:52.330
and we're still working
on things at the T.

00:59:52.330 --> 00:59:56.770
I was involved from the time
we were in discovery on.

00:59:56.770 --> 00:59:59.470
You can find places
where you can fit.

00:59:59.470 --> 01:00:01.950
Where you can really,
really make a difference

01:00:01.950 --> 01:00:04.540
